data.description: Welcome to this exceptional home that has been featured in the prestigious Parade of Homes! Nestled in a picturesque country setting on nearly 2 acres, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury, space, and functionality. Located close to schools and shopping, this property is an oasis of tranquility with easy access to everyday conveniences. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open floor plan designed for both family living and entertaining. In the family room you will find vaulted ceilings with wood beams, a cozy stone fireplace, and built in cabinets. The custom Amish cabinets and granite countertops in the kitchen are a chef's dream. Stainless steel appliances and a well-appointed breakfast bar create a perfect setting for culinary creations. The adjoining eat-in area offers a great space for casual meals, and the planning desk is a convenient bonus.The split bedroom design ensures privacy, with the private owner's suite featuring direct access to the back porch. As you step in the backyard to unwind, you will find a covered porch with entertainment center, a hot tub, and fiberglass sports pool with an automatic cover, ensuring safety and convenience.  This is the ideal spot to host gatherings and enjoy the beautiful outdoor space in any weather.In addition to the remarkable home, this property boasts a massive 56x40 pole barn, providing ample space for your hobbies, storage, or workshop needs. In the pole barn, you will find a 25 x 18 living space and a full bath. The pole barn was made on a concreate foundation and has 10 x 14 overhead doors. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own. Experience the perfect blend of country living and modern luxury!
